claim.claim-text:
12. A system, comprising:
a sensor comprising a portable memory storing code;
a pulse oximeter, comprising:
a sensor port;
an oximeter memory configured to store software; and
a processor configured to execute an application configured to read the code stored on the portable memory when the portable memory is coupled to the sensor port and update the software on the oximeter memory based on the code stored on the portable memory, wherein the code comprises a pulse oximetry algorithm configured to facilitate calculation of patient parameter values, and wherein the updated software remains stored on the oximetry memory after the sensor is disconnected from the pulse oximeter and is available for use with at least one sensor that is subsequently used with the pulse oximeter, and wherein the processor is configured to determine a patient parameter based at least in part upon the updated software.
